A three server web infrastructure that hosts the website www.foobar.com that is secured, serve encrypted traffic, and be monitored. It covers:
3 firewalls
1 SSL certificate to serve www.foobar.com over HTTPS
3 monitoring clients (data collector for Sumologic or other monitoring services)

